{"title":"四烈士的血，没有白流！——为纪念“一二一”而作——","authors":["马丁"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":12,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"四烈士的血，没有白流！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——为纪念“一二一”而作——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从昆明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从民主堡垒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出发！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“一二·一”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国学生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑起“五四”遗留下来的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开始"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新的进军。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暴徒，特务"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁棍、手榴弹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向西南“联大”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"围击，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"校门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被劈倒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四烈士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就以自己的血肉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"填上去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——堵住！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是生与死的搏斗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是迎向敌人的火网"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爆炸掉身躯的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搏斗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于再"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李鲁连"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倒下了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张华昌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"潘琰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶上去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以最崇高的同志爱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抢救自己的兄弟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以不可抑屈的头颅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碰击敌人的刀、枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弹片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横飞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脑浆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淌流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暴徒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拔出尖刀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再向倒地的兄弟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屠杀……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十七岁的张华昌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"继着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牺牲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最英勇的潘琰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"继着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倒下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四烈士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就这样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热血喷溅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国学生的生路！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“同学们，团结呀！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是潘琰烈士临死的呼喊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是“一二·一”递给我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"们的信号！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的知识分子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从八年抗战的重压里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挺立起来了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的知识分子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重新"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇敢地组织和行动！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“争民主！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“反内战！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从昆明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“一二·一”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一把狂烧的火炬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举向前面！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是工农群众的阵地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是总攻击的队伍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四烈士的血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"命令我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加速步武！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四个战斗的历程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长途的斑斑的血迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从“一二·一”到“一二·卅”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到“六·二”到“七·五”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们终于走到了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走到了新中国的大路！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在四烈士的光辉的照耀里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在南方胜利的进军里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在中华人民共和国的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诞生里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山巅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轰响着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新时代的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利之歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼唱了："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“四烈士呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们的血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有白流”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}